author: Peter Jacobs
title: Trump: It's 'fake news' that a reporter just opened his mailbox and found my tax returns
text:
President Donald Trump attacked an MSNBC report on his tax returns Wednesday morning, calling it "FAKE NEWS!" that a reporter found the president's tax returns in his mailbox.
The reporter who got Trump's 2005 tax return openly questioned whether Trump could have leaked it himself People lost their minds on Twitter as Rachel Maddow dragged out her own story on Trump's taxes Trump releases some 2005 tax info ahead of Rachel Maddow report Read more...
